  "DescIdentified": {
    "type": "cexolocstring",
    "value": {
      "0": "This blade belonged to Dabbar, a long dead servant to Bhaal that exercised control over his minions in the most brutal of ways. In addition to strengthening the mind against the guile of others, the sword absorbs life energy from an opponent with each successful hit, healing the user.\n\nDabbar considered it a failure of his officers if he returned from battle in less than perfect health, and as the rest of the company watched, he would administer beatings until fully healed."
